title: Travel time estimates
text:

title: About
text:
This website displays the data from the analysis of travel times in select Madison (Wisconsin) corridors. The main repository for the project is at https://github.com/vgXhc/travel_time_estimates
Author/contact: Harald Kliems (kliems@proton.me)
